room_title: Escape room "Interrogation" by Escape Rooms HQ in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description:
You’ve been framed for a crime you didn’t commit. Apparently, you tried to steal a top-secret superconductor called “Liquid X”. You and your cohorts have been brought in to be interrogated. On the surface, this seems like a bad thing. The Detectives think your guilt is a foregone conclusion.
But you have a unique opportunity. If you can find the evidence they have against you and the true culprit, you just might avoid prison.
